## 5. Report


```{.r .cell-code}
trial |>
  tbl_summary(
    by = arm,
    statistic = list(all_continuous() ~ "{mean} ({sd})"),
    digits    = all_continuous() ~ 1,
    label     = list(sbp_change = "Change in SBP (mmHg)")
  ) |>
  add_p() |>
  modify_caption("**Table 1. Change in systolic blood pressure, by arm.**")
```

